data.description: Beautiful Corner lot in Canyon East! Open Style with Modern Design kitchen with flat granite island and double ovens. The living room is great sized with outstanding fireplace and built in bookshelves. Throughout the house is 10 ft ceilings and 8 ft doors. The isolated master with ensuite features separate shower and tub and large walk in closet. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms are good sized with large closets and share a full hall bath. Schedule your showing today!!
